column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,s. zErr as errredshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid,f.z,f. zErr,GN.distance  FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#.,#, #) AS GN  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = GN.objID  join Photoz as f ON f.objid = GN.objID
